Session Control
-----------------
tmux 	       Start a new session
tmux attach    Re-attach a detached session
tmux attach -d Re-attach a detached session
               (and detach it from elsewhere)

Pane Control
------------------
Ctrl-B " 	Split pane horizontally
Ctrl-B % 	Split pane vertically
Ctrl-B o 	Next pane
Ctrl-B ; 	Previous pane
Ctrl-B x 	Kill current pane
Ctrl-B ! 	Kill all panes but the current one
Ctrl-B Ctrl-O 	Swap panes
Ctrl-B t 	Display clock
Ctrl-B q 	Transpose two letters
            (delete and paste)

Window Control
----------------
Ctrl-B c 	Create new window
Ctrl-B d 	Detach from session
Ctrl-B , 	Rename a window
Ctrl-B w 	List windows
Ctrl-B [0-9] Switch Window
